query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.Gender = 1
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.Gender = 2
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.Gender not in (1, 2)
